com.foresee.sdk.common.instrumentation

Annotation Type IgnorePageViews


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface IgnorePageViews
    Ignores unwanted page views Any activity's onResume event will cause an increment of the page view count in the ForeSee SDK. When dealing with full-screen fragments it is often best to use the manual ForeSee.incrementPageViews method on the fragment's onResume method. In those cases this will allow you to suppress the page view increment for the containing activity. Use this if you notice the page view count is larger than expected from your manual page view increments
